## 🎯 Learning Outcomes  

- Learned how to **apply responsive design principles** using media queries.  
- Gained experience in building **interactive web components** (quiz & carousel).  
- Practiced **API integration** to fetch and display **real-time data dynamically**.  
- Improved skills in **JavaScript event handling, DOM manipulation, and error handling**.  
- Strengthened ability to **organize project structure** for scalability.  



